name: Large Coil
description: Original marker and pen drawing on cold pressed watercolor paper.  Image is 5 by 7 in.  and comes in a 8 by 10 mat, as well as a clear display bag.  I'm really having fun exploring the marker media, and look forward to posting many more of these over the next year.

name: February Print
description: Every month of 2013 I will be releasing a limited edition print.  Each print is an edition of 5.  They are printed on a heavier parchment paper and are 35 by 23 in., so pretty big.  Because of the small scale run I'm also able to paint directly on each print.  So each print is a bit different and an original in it's own right.  This also means the print you get might have some slight variations from the one pictured (mainly in the bright red ink overlay).  All come signed and numbered.

name: Sketch Book
description:
A collection of sketches from 2008-2010.  So it's a bit older, but it's probably the only collection of sketches I'm going to put out anytime soon.  36 pages.  black and white, with a color cover.  There's only a handful left, and they won't be reprinted.  Comes signed.  

*This is sold as a collection of work to be used as reference and inspiration, but not as flash.  So please to not use these designs to copy for tattoos.  Many of them have been done as custom pieces on very good clients over the years, and it would be disrespecting them as well as myself to reproduce any designs as tattoos.
